%% Models as a Service - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User/Client
    participant GW as maas-default-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Terminate
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>(Kuadrant AuthPolicy)
    participant Limitador as Limitador<br/>(TokenRateLimitPolicy)
    participant MaaS as maas-api<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP (optional)
    participant LLM as LLMInferenceService<br/>Backend

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
    Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Token Issuance (POST /v1/tokens or /v1/api-keys)
    Client->>GW: POST /maas-api/v1/tokens<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OpenShift identity)
    GW->>Authorino: Evaluate maas-api-auth-policy
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>(audiences: kubernetes.default.svc)
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Identity confirmed
    Authorino-->>GW: Set X-MaaS-Username + X-MaaS-Group
    GW->>MaaS: Forward request<br/>Headers: X-MaaS-Username, X-MaaS-Group
    MaaS->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace (if needed)<br/>Create ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI-->>MaaS: SA created
    MaaS->>K8sAPI: TokenRequest<br/>(audience: maas-default-gateway-sa)
    K8sAPI-->>MaaS: JWT SA Token
    opt External Storage Mode
        MaaS->>PG: Store API key metadata
        PG-->>MaaS: Confirmed
    end
    MaaS-->>GW: JWT SA Token in response
    GW-->>Client: 200 OK + Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Model Discovery (GET /v1/models)
    Client->>GW: GET /v1/models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    GW->>Authorino: Evaluate auth policy
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Identity confirmed
    GW->>MaaS: Forward with identity headers
    Note over MaaS: List LLMInferenceServices<br/>from informer cache
    MaaS->>GW: Authorization loopback check<br/>GET model endpoint (TLS, InsecureSkipVerify)
    GW-->>MaaS: Auth result per model
    MaaS-->>GW: OpenAI-compatible model list
    GW-->>Client: 200 OK + Model List
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 3: Model Inference with Rate Limiting
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (MaaS-issued SA token)
    GW->>Authorino: Evaluate gateway-auth-policy
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>(audience: maas-default-gateway-sa)
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Identity confirmed
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(llminferenceservices)
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Authorized
    Authorino->>MaaS: POST /v1/tiers/lookup<br/>(cached 300s)
    MaaS-->>Authorino: Tier: premium
    GW->>Limitador: Check token rate limit<br/>(premium: 50000 tokens/min)
    Limitador-->>GW: Allowed
    GW->>LLM: Forward inference request<br/>Proxied Bearer Token
    LLM-->>GW: Inference response
    GW-->>Client: 200 OK + Completion
    end
